OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, A sub-postmaster claims a new version  
OL,6, of the Horizon system has left him more
OL,7, than #2,900 in debt.                   
OL,9,FFor years, hundreds of sub-postmasters 
OL,10,Fwere wrongly accused of stealing money 
OL,11,Fdue to incorrect data being provided by
OL,12,Fthe computer system.                   
OL,14,FSheffield sub-postmaster Nasar Raoof   
OL,15,Fsaid the software had since been       
OL,16,Fupdated but was still causing problems.
OL,18,FA Post Office spokesperson said the new
OL,19,FHorizon version was "robust" and that  
OL,20,Ftraining had been offered to Mr Raoof. 
